headline.main: Parents: Bar Release of Video of UConn Student's Death
headline.print_headline: Parents: Bar Release of Video of UConn Student's Death

lead_paragraph: The parents of a University of Connecticut student who died after being run over by a campus fire department vehicle are asking a judge to prohibit public release of a surveillance video of the accident, saying it would be offensive and upset her family.
